title: Giorgio Armani Acqua Di Gio Profondo for Men Eau De Parfum Spray 2.5 Ounces
features: An aromatic fougere fragrance for modern men
Fresh, clean, watery, leafy, earthy & uplifting
Top notes are sea tones, aquozone, bergamot & green mandarin
Middle notes are rosemary, lavender, cypress & mastic or lentisque
Base notes are amber, mineral accord, patchouli & musk
Suitable for spring or summer wear
description: What it is: An eau de parfum that enhances the original signature of Acqua di Giò with a profound, almost primary minerality.Fragrance story: Profondo explores a different dimension of Acqua di Giò's origins: the deep sea. Serene yet mysterious, it opens with salty marine notes before melting into invigorating essences of cypress, lavender and rosemary. The depths of the sea are expressed through patchouli and musk notes, which leave a long-lasting, mysterious trail.Style: Aquatic fougère.
